- What?

305
00:31:59,476 --> 00:32:01,516
Ella, fetch.

306
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:11,277
Atta girl. I know it's heavy. You can do it.

307
00:32:12,114 --> 00:32:15,614
Come on. Stretch for it. Make it burn.

