00:44:45,306 --> 00:44:47,346
Maryanne!

447
00:44:47,892 --> 00:44:51,510
Maryanne! Maryanne!

448
00:44:51,646 --> 00:44:53,306
Maryanne!

449
00:44:57,485 --> 00:45:00,155
Maryanne! Maryanne!

450
00:45:15,837 --> 00:45:17,877
God give me strength.

451
00:45:27,891 --> 00:45:30,465
Get rid of that bird, Maryanne.

